      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like both sides do it though. like one side says everything is fake news to hide their own stuff, but the other side also uses \"fact checkers\" to label things they don't like as misinformation. don't you think it's pretty much just a tool used by anyone in power to control the narrative?",
